OL,3,CInspections of coastal defences met
OL,4,Cwith concern by seafront businesses
OL,6,FInspections of Guernsey's sea defences
OL,7,Fbegan today (Monday 18 November) with
OL,8,Fa view to allocating a budget for
OL,9,Ffuture maintenance plans.
OL,11,FThe condition of eight coastal sites -
OL,12,Fthe Imperial Slipway, Fort Grey,
OL,13,FRocquaine, Grand Port, l'Eree,
OL,14,FPerelle, Cobo, and Pembroke - will be
OL,15,Fexamined over the course of the next
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,18,FHowever, some islanders fear the
OL,19,Finspections are not being done in the
OL,20,Fcorrect places.
