OL,3,CInspections of coastal defences met
OL,4,Cwith concern by seafront businesses
OL,6,FHe is calling for the States to invest
OL,7,Fin coastal defences in town.
OL,9,FHe says: "I just think it's not going
OL,10,Faway as a problem. For the sake of a
OL,11,Fsmall granite wall, maybe a foot high.
OL,12,FTides come to ten meters, maybe 10.5
OL,13,Fso you'd only have to go up a meter to
OL,14,Fstop the water coming over."
OL,16,FMarco Tesigni, States of Guernsey
OL,17,FInfrastructure Officer, says the
OL,18,Finspections are targeted at sites
OL,19,Fwhere the States can act proactively
OL,20,Fagainst erosion in the future.
