OL,3,CInspections of coastal defences met
OL,4,Cwith concern by seafront businesses
OL,6,FThe West Coast sites are considered to
OL,7,Fbe important ones that provide direct
OL,8,Fprotection to the land behind them
OL,9,Ffrom coastal flooding.
OL,11,FSome of these sites have already had
OL,12,Fto have maintenance carried out: such
OL,13,Fas at Perelle, where the crumbling sea
OL,14,Fwall has recently been repaired.
