OL,3,CInspections of coastal defences met
OL,4,Cwith concern by seafront businesses
OL,6,FHe adds: "It's all about priority and
OL,7,Fmoney only goes so far. We have to
OL,8,Fprioritise with the funds that we've
OL,9,Fgot. These are areas that we feel -
OL,10,Fand the engineers who have the
OL,11,Ftechnical knowledge feel - we should
OL,12,Fprioritise now."
